</code></pre> <p>To add our development environment we'll want to get our account identifier.  </p> <p>In the notebook we'll have to update our connectection parameters. Once pasted we'll make sure we replace the <code>.</code> with a <code>-</code> otherwise it won't connect to the account.</p>  Setup Example <pre><code>connection_parameters = {
